#: ../../language/error_codes/E4175.md:1
msgid "E4175"
msgstr "E4175"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4175.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `as_not_trait_object`."
msgstr "编译器诊断名称：`as_not_trait_object`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4175.md:5
msgid "The right-hand side of `as` is not a trait object type."
msgstr "`as` 右侧不是 trait 对象类型。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4175.md:7
msgid ""
"MoonBit uses `as &Trait` to convert a value to a trait object. The target"
" type must therefore be a trait object type such as `&Show`, not an "
"ordinary concrete type, type parameter, or package type."
msgstr ""
"MoonBit 使用 `as &Trait` 将值转换为 trait 对象。因此目标类型必须是 `&Show` 这"
"样的 trait 对象类型，而不是普通的具体类型、类型参数或包类型。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4175.md:11
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4175.md:13
msgid ""
"fn invalid_cast() -> Unit {\n"
"  let _ = 1 as Int\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4175.md:17
msgid ""
"`Int` is a concrete type, not a trait object type, so it cannot be used "
"on the right-hand side of `as`."
msgstr "`Int` 是具体类型，不是 trait 对象类型，因此不能用在 `as` 的右侧。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4175.md:20
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4175.md:22
msgid ""
"Use `as &Trait` when you want a trait object. If you only need a type "
"annotation, write the expected type as an annotation instead of using "
"`as`."
msgstr ""
"如果需要 trait 对象，请使用 `as &Trait`。如果只需要类型标注，请将期望类型写成"
"标注，而不是使用 `as`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4175.md:25
msgid ""
"fn show_value() -> Unit {\n"
"  let value = 1 as &Show\n"
"  println(value)\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

